RENDER FORMAT
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Choose the format that best describes the primary structure of the fact's content.
A fact with mixed content (e.g. intro paragraph + bullets) takes the dominant format.

  paragraph       — fact is primarily prose (one or more paragraphs)
  bullet          — fact is primarily a bulleted list (with or without an intro line or heading)
  numbered-step   — fact is primarily a numbered list of steps
  definition-entry — fact is a **Term:** definition pair

