AUDIENCE HINT
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Leave audience_hint empty [] unless this specific fact explicitly targets a narrower
audience than the document default. Set to ["students"], ["staff"], or ["parents"]
only when the source text makes the target audience explicit.
Example: "From Year 9 upwards, students are responsible for their own medication."
→ audience_hint: ["students"]

